<s> the main purpose for use to use OIDs in URIs is in XML signatures.  </s>
<s> there we will need to use OIDs in form of URIs to refer to policies, other documents, ... that are already present and hav an OID. because XML has the great advantage that it is plain text, it can be read (debugged) by humans by just viewing it with any text editor.  </s>
<s> URIs are normally in form that you can roughly get an idea what's behind it.  </s>
<s> if we just use the pure number presentation of OIDs, i think (and others share this opinion) we are going to lose one advantage.  </s>
